Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.44,0:00:29.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还要多久我们才能使用钻头？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How much longer till we can use the drill?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.02,0:00:32.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}其实，有了我们从月球基地得到的新的坐标，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, with the new coordinates we got from the moonbase,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.84,0:00:33.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们应该可以行动了\N{\fnArial\fs48}we should be ready to go.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.17,0:00:36.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我们真的该先进行一些测试\N{\fnArial\fs48}But we really should perform a few tests first.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.20,0:00:39.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.73,0:00:42.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.40,0:00:44.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我得跟你谈谈\N{\fnArial\fs48}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.84,0:00:46.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，好啊，没问题\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, yeah. Sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么我们要在这个坏掉的载具里？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why are we in this broken-down vehicle?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.57,0:00:52.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我想问你一下...\N{\fnArial\fs48}I wanted to ask you...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.46,0:00:55.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}关于钻石吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}About the diamonds?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.26,0:00:56.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.13,0:00:59.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不知道其他人是怎么跟你说的，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know what the others have told you,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.26,0:01:00.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但钻石掌权时有原因的\N{\fnArial\fs48}but there's a reason they're in charge.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.26,0:01:02.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why's that?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.33,0:01:04.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们客观上来讲要比我们更优秀\N{\fnArial\fs48}They're objectively better than us.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.17,0:01:06.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}每个宝石人都有自己的优势与弱点-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Every gem has their strengths and weaknesses --
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.23,0:01:07.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但她们不是\N{\fnArial\fs48}but not them.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.53,0:01:10.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们是绝对，完全，肯定无瑕的存在！\N{\fnArial\fs48}They're absolutely, totally, completely flawless beings!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:10.84,0:01:13.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}尤其是我的钻石-黄钻石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Especially my diamond -- yellow diamond.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.90,0:01:16.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}最完美，最理性，理智，\N{\fnArial\fs48}The most perfect, the most reasonable, rational,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.34,0:01:18.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}完美的决策者-放到全宇宙也是\N{\fnArial\fs48}efficient decider ever to exist in the Universe.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.28,0:01:21.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你对她真是忠诚啊，不是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're really loyal to her, aren't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.68,0:01:23.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我怎么可能不呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How could I not be?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们间也许有小小的休战协议，\N{\fnArial\fs48}We might have our little truce,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.84,0:01:27.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我永远不会背叛我服务的宝石人的\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I'll never forsake the gem I was made for.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那很好，因为她就在你背后\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's good, because she's right behind you.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.73,0:01:31.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.60,0:01:34.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊，不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.55,0:01:35.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别挣扎了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Save your strength!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.17,0:01:37.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你面对的是地球\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're up against one of the earth's
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.37,0:01:39.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}最伟大的囚禁技术之一-\N{\fnArial\fs48}greatest trapping technologies --
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.26,0:01:41.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}儿童安全锁！\N{\fnArial\fs48}the child safety lock!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.64,0:01:43.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不！不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No! No!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.13,0:01:47.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你怎么能这样对我-伟大而可爱的橄榄石？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}How could you do this to me -- the great and lovable Peridot?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.48,0:01:51.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我以为我们总算是朋友了，就像你希望的那样！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought we were finally friends, like you wanted!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.91,0:01:54.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我看到你将这个偷偷带出了月球基地\N{\fnArial\fs48}I saw you sneak this off the moon base
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.15,0:01:55.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就在没人注意的时候！\N{\fnArial\fs48}while no one else was looking!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.77,0:01:57.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是什么？从实招来！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is it? Tell me!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.91,0:01:59.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这没什么特别的...\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's nothing special...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且绝对不重要！\N{\fnArial\fs48}And definitely not important at all!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.86,0:02:03.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.00,0:02:06.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那我为什么不砸了它呢？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Then why don't I just smash it?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.57,0:02:08.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不不不不，等等！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, no, no, no, wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.53,0:02:09.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，听着\N{\fnArial\fs48}All right, look.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.84,0:02:12.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我有个计划，容许我解释一下\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have a plan. Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是个...通讯器\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's... A communicator.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.55,0:02:17.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}用来快速的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Meant for the express purpose
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.71,0:02:19.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}与母世界的钻石通讯\N{\fnArial\fs48}of contacting the diamonds back on homeworld.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你仍然在试图与母世界联系？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're still trying to contact homeworld?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.86,0:02:24.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对，当然！我想通了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes. Of course! I figured it out!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.55,0:02:27.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们这群幼稚的草包总是试图保护地球，\N{\fnArial\fs48}You simple clods keep trying to protect the earth,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但你们什么事都做不对！\N{\fnArial\fs48}but you can't do anything right!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我自己都被带偏了-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I let myself get carried away, too --
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.98,0:02:34.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}欢笑，歌唱，建造我们的小小机器！\N{\fnArial\fs48}laughing, singing, building our little machine!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但你看不出来吗？这都没有用！\N{\fnArial\fs48}But don't you see? None of that matters!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真正重要的是我对黄钻石有所贡献！\N{\fnArial\fs48}All that matters is that I'm of use to yellow diamond!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.11,0:02:43.49,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个星球可以对黄钻石有所贡献！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This planet can be of use to yellow diamond!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.75,0:02:46.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我必须要联系她-向她说明我所发现的情况！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I must contact her -- to reveal what I've discovered!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但是钻石都很坏啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}But the diamonds are bad!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们并不在乎地球\N{\fnArial\fs48}They don't care about the earth.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们之前想将它掏空，\N{\fnArial\fs48}They wanted to hollow it out,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而现在她们又要用融合簇将地球炸毁！\N{\fnArial\fs48}and now they want to blow it up with the cluster!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对，对！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就是这个！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's the point!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.62,0:02:56.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为何我总是不顾反对的支持你！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why do I keep sticking my neck out for you!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你永远也不会站到我们这边！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're never gonna be on our side!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴，紫晶，珍珠！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet, Amethyst, Pearl!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，别-别叫她们！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, no -- don't get them!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}放我走吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Release me!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.15,0:03:13.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她从月球基地拿了一个\N{\fnArial\fs48}She took a direct line to the diamonds
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}与钻石的直连通讯器？\N{\fnArial\fs48}from the moon base?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.31,0:03:16.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她在想什么啊？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What was she thinking?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}天哪，就算我们一起经历了这么多，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Man, after everything we've gone through,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她仍然想搞事情\N{\fnArial\fs48}she's still out to get us.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.08,0:03:24.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，我要收回我给她起的所有炫酷外号\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, I'm taking back all my cool nicknames for her.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.84,0:03:27.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}再见了，“橄榄”和“橄石”\N{\fnArial\fs48}So long "Perry" and "p-dot."
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你好，“橄”...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hello, p...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊！我太生气了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah! I'm too mad!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.26,0:03:33.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我以后再想想吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll think of something later!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我看她现在搞清楚什么是喇叭了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I see she knows what a horn is now.
Dialogue: 600,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.50,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}史蒂文的动作与装束与《南方公园》的肯尼相同
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你给她了许多的信任\N{\fnArial\fs48}You offered her a lot of your trust.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I did!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}结果却糊了我一脸\N{\fnArial\fs48}And it blew up in my face.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们已经保护地球\N{\fnArial\fs48}You guys have been protecting the earth
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}几千年了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}for thousands of years!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她本可能【破坏掉这一切-\N{\fnArial\fs48}She could have destroyed all of that --
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一整个地球！\N{\fnArial\fs48}a whole earth!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么我以为我能改变她的的想法？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why did I think I could change her mind?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，我知道，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh. I know, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我想你不能，像是，进入别人的头脑\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I guess you can't, like, get into other people's heads
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}然后改变她们的想法\N{\fnArial\fs48}and change what they think.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，也许我们可以？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, maybe we can?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果我们缩得非常小，\N{\fnArial\fs48}If we just shrink down really little,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们就能进入-不不不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}we can get in -- no, no, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不想命令她做该做的事\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't want to tell her what to do.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.15,0:04:15.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她应该要理解，不是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}She should just know, shouldn't she?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你相信任何人都能洗，这很好，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's good you believe in everyone, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.11,0:04:19.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就像你母亲，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Like your mother,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}相比我们你似乎有多一点的耐心\N{\fnArial\fs48}you seem to have a little more patience than the rest of us.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.66,0:04:26.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但事实是不是所有人配得上这种耐心\N{\fnArial\fs48}But the truth is not everyone deserves that patience.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.63,0:04:27.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}往好处想-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look on the bright side --
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.17,0:04:29.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}至少你把这个从她手里拿走了\N{\fnArial\fs48}at least you got this thing away from her
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}避免了她可能制造的破坏\N{\fnArial\fs48}before she did any real damage.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.31,0:04:32.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.81,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}自由！自由！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Free, free!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她怎么逃脱的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How did she escape?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢！笨蛋！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh! Fools!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.98,0:04:49.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你的不可见旋转护盾可阻挡不了我-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Your invisible rotary shield was no match for me --
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.59,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只要我使用逻辑的话！\N{\fnArial\fs48}once I applied logic!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.42,0:04:56.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在我要正确的完成这一切！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now I'm gonna do this right!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃！看到了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh! See?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们没人知道自己在做什么！\N{\fnArial\fs48}None of you know what you're doing!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，吼吼吼！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh-ho ho-kay!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我早就准备好了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've been ready for this!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快上车！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Get in.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where's Steven?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}垃圾橄榄石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stupid Peridot!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}垃圾巨型机器人！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stupid giant robot!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.15,0:05:23.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，为何，哦，为何我非得鼓励她？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, why, oh, why did I have to encourage her?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没时间难受了\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's no time for feeling horrible.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们得在橄榄石与黄钻石取得联系前抓住她！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We have to catch Peridot before she contacts yellow diamond!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.57,0:05:30.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没错\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你尽可在回到神庙后难受个够\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can feel horrible all you want back at the temple.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么样，鼻涕石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's up, peri-snot?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}说得好，紫晶！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Good one, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.55,0:05:58.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}猛犬扑堆！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dog pile!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.53,0:05:59.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.77,0:06:08.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你可别想逃走！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're not getting away with it!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我信任过你！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I trusted you!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我花了那么多时间和你交流，心怀期待，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I spent all that time bonding and hoping
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}关怀备至！\N{\fnArial\fs48}and caring about you!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你也没想清楚！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You don't get it, either!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这就是你的...\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is your whole...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}问题！\N{\fnArial\fs48}...problem!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你的感性驱散了理性！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Your emotions rule out reason!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.73,0:06:29.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会完成该完成的工作！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I will do what has to be done!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.89,0:06:30.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她会解决这个的\N{\fnArial\fs48}She'll sort this out.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这里是黄钻石控制室\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is the yellow diamond control room.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是又一个珍珠吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is that another Pearl?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她是谁？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who is she?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不是所有珍珠都认识彼此的，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not all pearls know each other, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是谁授权你进行此次通话的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who authorized you to make this call?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没有人\N{\fnArial\fs48}No one.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但-但这是紧急情况！\N{\fnArial\fs48}B-but it's an emergency!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这不是使用\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's no excuse to use
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}钻石直连通信通道的借口！\N{\fnArial\fs48}the direct diamond communication channel!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是的，我的钻石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, my diamond?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么有人在钻石专线上？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why is there someone on the diamond line?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不清楚！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我刚准备告诉她-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was just about to tell her that --
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我来接管吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is that...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}黄...钻石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yellow... Diamond.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的钻石！橄榄石来此报告！\N{\fnArial\fs48}My diamond! Peridot reporting in!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哪个橄榄石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Which Peridot?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.66,0:07:25.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}切-切面2f5l，切割5xg\N{\fnArial\fs48}F-facet 2f5l, cut 5xg.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我很抱歉用这种方法与您联系\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sorry to contact you this way,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但所有其他的通讯手段\N{\fnArial\fs48}but all other forms of communication
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}都被破坏了，而且-\N{\fnArial\fs48}have been destroyed and --
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看来你的任务进度滞后了...\N{\fnArial\fs48}this says you're behind schedule on your mission to...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}地球怎么样了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How is the earth?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那里充满了生命！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's full of life!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有机生命\N{\fnArial\fs48}Organic life.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么我分配给你的铁石英呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}And where is the Jasper I assigned you?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有为什么你不从飞船上通话呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}And why aren't you calling from the ship?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，嗯...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, hmm...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}飞船被摧毁了\N{\fnArial\fs48}The ship was destroyed.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.31,0:07:50.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}被谁？\N{\fnArial\fs48}By whom?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它-它-它是被...\N{\fnArial\fs48}It -- it -- it was destroyed by...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.55,0:07:56.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没人干的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No one!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}发生了一场意外...\N{\fnArial\fs48}There was an accident...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.67,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就在我们着陆时\N{\fnArial\fs48}While we were landing.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.93,0:08:05.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会告知你上司你的无能的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll inform your manager of your incompetence.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有，融合簇的状态呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}And what is the status of the cluster?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}融合簇会很快孵化的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}The cluster will emerge shortly!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.97,0:08:12.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好\N{\fnArial\fs48}Good.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们总算能从那可悲的星球榨取出一点点成果了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We'll finally get some use out of that miserable planet.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.88,0:08:17.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谢谢你的报告，橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thank you for your report, Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}会有一艘飞船前往你的位置\N{\fnArial\fs48}There'll be a ship heading to your location
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}带你前往下一项任务\N{\fnArial\fs48}to take you to your next assignment.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.86,0:08:21.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等下！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我不会为了用\N{\fnArial\fs48}I -- I wouldn't have called
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}报告浪费您的时间而进行通话的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}just to waste your time with a report!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你已经是了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You already have.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，我是指，我进行通话的原因，\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, I mean, the reason I've called,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.35,0:08:32.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真正的原因是...\N{\fnArial\fs48}the real reason is...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.15,0:08:35.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我相信我们应该终止融合簇！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I believe we should terminate the cluster!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个世界的有机生态系统创造了独有的资源\N{\fnArial\fs48}The organic ecosystem creates resources unique to this world.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们不能牺牲掉所有的可能性\N{\fnArial\fs48}We can't sacrifice all that potential
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就为了一个超级武器！\N{\fnArial\fs48}just for one geo-weapon!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我想告诉您一些我想到的方案\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'd like to tell you some plans I came up with
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}用来利用这个星球而不干扰当地的-\N{\fnArial\fs48}to utilize the planet without disrupting the local --
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我听够了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.88,0:08:54.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不在乎潜力和资源\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't care about potential and resources.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.31,0:08:55.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}蛤？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我想要我的融合簇，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I want my cluster,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且我想让那个星球死掉\N{\fnArial\fs48}and I want that planet to die.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只需要让那发生\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just make that happen.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.00,0:09:03.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.82,0:09:04.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.08,0:09:08.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是在质疑我的权威吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you questioning my authority?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只是在怀疑您的客观性，我的钻石\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm questioning your objectivity, my diamond.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.13,0:09:11.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}牛啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你真是胆大啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You are out of line.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只是认为-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just think --
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.39,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不在乎\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm not interested
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一个橄榄石的卑微的想法\N{\fnArial\fs48}in the puny thoughts of a Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.08,0:09:21.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但-\N{\fnArial\fs48}But --
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.09,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你的出现已经冒犯了这个频道与我的时间，\N{\fnArial\fs48}you have disrespected this channel and my time with your presence,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而你应该\N{\fnArial\fs48}and you would do well to
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.04,0:09:26.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但是\N{\fnArial\fs48}but
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.23,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}闭上嘴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.24,0:09:32.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你在这个任务的每个阶段都失败了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You have failed at every stage of this mission.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你救赎自己的唯一机会\N{\fnArial\fs48}Your only chance to redeem yourself
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.02,0:09:37.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就是遵守这个简单的命令-\N{\fnArial\fs48}is to obey this simple order --
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你要让融合簇继续生长！\N{\fnArial\fs48}you are to leave the cluster to grow!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它会拆碎地球，\N{\fnArial\fs48}It will tear apart the earth,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.84,0:09:44.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而我也会感受到巨大的满足\N{\fnArial\fs48}and I will take immense satisfaction
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}将那个丑恶的石头\N{\fnArial\fs48}in erasing that hideous rock
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}从我的星图上抹去！\N{\fnArial\fs48}off of our star maps!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}清楚吗？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is that clear?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.60,0:09:52.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不会做的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I won't do it!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.46,0:09:53.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我可以肯定的告诉你\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can tell you with certainty
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个星球上有很多值得保护的东西！\N{\fnArial\fs48}that there are things on this planet worth protecting!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你对地球又了解什么 ？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do you know about the earth?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.48,0:10:03.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}显然比你要多，你个草包！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Apparently more than you, you clod!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，橄榄石，结束！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, Peridot, out!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.28,0:10:13.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那真是太棒了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That was amazing!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不敢相信我刚才做了那个\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't believe I just did that.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我之前真错误的理解你真错误的对待我了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was so wrong about being so wrong about you!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不敢相信我刚才做了那个\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't believe I just did that.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你认为你能改变她的想法\N{\fnArial\fs48}You thought you could change her mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}黄B被橄榄屌干了个底朝天！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yellow d got torn down by the peridactyl!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.97,0:10:27.79,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃～\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.13,0:10:29.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们有人能拿这个嘛？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can one of you take this?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}因为它可以被遥控引爆\N{\fnArial\fs48}Because it can be remotely detonated.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们该怎么阻止它？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How do we stop it?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.88,0:10:36.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}赶紧丢掉它吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just get rid of it!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，给你，紫晶！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, here, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我又该拿它怎么办？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What am I supposed to do with it?!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我以为我能跟她讲道理\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought I could reason with her.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没错，你真的把她气疯了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, you really made her mad.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}然后你当面顶撞了她\N{\fnArial\fs48}And then you insulted her to her face.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道这意味着什么吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是我家乡的叛徒\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm a traitor to my homeworld.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.77,0:11:00.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是个水晶战士了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're a Crystal Gem!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不论你愿不愿意！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦～\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh!
